    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> How do we ensure *-hooks packages use parallel versioning?\r\n\r\nAs they depend on each other, the version number should be chosen in parallel, although I believe it's possible for a feature in only hooks-web for example requiring a manual intervention for hooks-web. Not sure if you imagine a solution without manual work?",
