    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "> As they depend on each other, the version number should be chosen in parallel\r\n\r\nA change in `react-instantsearch-hooks-server` wouldn't result in an automatic bump in the others because no package depends on it.\r\n\r\n> Not sure if you imagine a solution without manual work?\r\n\r\nWe could write a script that checks all `package.json` of the Hooks packages and throws if the `version`s aren't the same?",
